13 §463.46. Special prestige license plates; Louisiana Quail Forever plate
14 * * *
15 B. The charge for this special license plate shall be twenty-six dollars, which
16 shall be assessed every two years in addition to the regular fee charged under the
17 provisions of R.S. 47:463. The department shall collect an annual royalty fee of fifty
18 dollars for this special prestige license plate that shall be disbursed in accordance
19 with Subsection C of this Section. This fee shall be in addition to the standard motor
20 vehicle license tax imposed by Article VII, Section 5 of the Constitution of
21 Louisiana, and a handling fee of three dollars and fifty cents for each plate to be
22 retained by the department to offset a portion of administrative costs.
